- The project will depict the trend of growth of Bitcoin market
- Language: Python, Python libraries: Pandas, MatplotLib
- Project tasks:
1. Loading the raw data from data from pdcoinmarketcap.com
2. Full dataset, filtering, and reproducibility
3. Discard the cryptocurrencies without a market capitalization
4. Comprare Bitcoin with the rest of the cryptocurrencies
5. Plot data
6. Explore this volatility in cryptocurrencies
7. Plot the top 10 biggest gainers and top 10 losers in market capitalization.
8. Check the weekly Series
9. Conslusion
